cara setup laravel ke server internal itsa:
1. ke cmder -> cd c:\laragon\www
2. git clone url_repo_github 
3. masuk ke folder caranya cd nama_folder_repo
4. copy file .env.example ke .env
5. edit file .env -> atur sesuai server internal itsa
6. sesuaikan file vite.config.js -> atur APP_URL sesuai server internal itsa
7. composer install 
8. npm install 
9. php artisan key:generate 
10. php artisan migrate
